'''加拿大一枝黄花'''（学名：{{lang|la|''Solidago canadensis''}}），又名'''黄莺'''、'''米兰'''、'''幸福花'''，为[[菊科|菊科]][[一枝黄花属|一枝黄花属]]多年生草本植物。原产[[北美地区|北美]]<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Dx9OpT113CUC&pg=PA118|publisher=University of Alberta|date=1996-12|isbn=978-0-88864-283-7|language=en|first=France|last=Royer|first2=Richard|last2=Dickinson|title=Wildflowers of Calgary and Southern Alberta|pages=118|access-date=2021-12-06|archive-date=2022-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220428135828/https://books.google.com/books?id=Dx9OpT113CUC&pg=PA118}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=THE BIOLOGY OF CANADIAN WEEDS.: 45. Solidago canadensis L.|url=http://www.nrcresearchpress.com/doi/10.4141/cjps80-194|last=Werner|first=Patricia A.|last2=Gross|first2=Ronald S.|date=1980-10-01|journal=Canadian Journal of Plant Science|issue=4|doi=10.4141/cjps80-194|volume=60|pages=1393–1409|language=en|issn=0008-4220|last3=Bradbury|first3=Ian K.|access-date=2021-12-06|archive-date=2020-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613195042/https://www.nrcresearchpress.com/doi/10.4141/cjps80-194}}</ref>，现在中国及欧洲的许多地方成为[[入侵物种|入侵植物]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=入侵的不速之客——加拿大一枝黄花|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/science/2019-07/14/c_138221105.htm|access-date=2021-12-06|date=2019-07-14|work=科普中国|publisher=新华网|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206014754/http://www.xinhuanet.com/science/2019-07/14/c_138221105.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=加拿大一枝黄花惊现重庆金海湾公园|url=http://cq.cqnews.net/html/2021-12/06/content_917303416610185216.html|access-date=2021-12-06|publisher=华龙网|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206144619/http://cq.cqnews.net/html/2021-12/06/content_917303416610185216.html}}</ref>。

其[[种加词|种加词]]“''canadensis''”意为“[[加拿大|加拿大]]的”。

